highlights.text: “反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1557 days straight.
“時候不早” by MC 張天賦 is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 57 spots at #131.
Anson Lo 盧瀚霆 has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “Lemonade” is the highest at #5.
